{"tid":1624560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位俾五分鐘入一入黎先","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:30:00.000Z","uid":76960,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e21b0c8a2e6c90c0e0e7bcbe21e03f97ada210a6","tid":1624560,"uid":76960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"首先呢個唔係分析post, 亦唔想長文<br />\n<br />\n只係想問下大家有冇覺得，經過尋晚，有一種拼命拉扯都好難將大家既意向集中一齊<br />\n<br />\n但樣野其實我地一路係有架，好似和理非日唔會有勇武決意果日勇武一樣<br />\n<br />\n無論幾時我地都係命運共同體，成敗係一齊承受/分享<br />\n<br />\n我開呢個post只係想大家入黎抖一抖氣，冷靜番個人<br />\n<br />\n面對同路人唔同既意見，唔好一言不合就屌先<br />\n<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心要熱，頭要冷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n條路岩岩先開始， 大家加油<br />\n<br />\n願榮光，歸香港"},{"pid":"45859aad6ba7f847f2ba697b616836c37934ab6b","tid":1624560,"uid":302501,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"革命唔係一朝一夕既事<br />\n香港人反抗"},{"pid":"027b332a243484a1adac5838f45f4a69454124eb","tid":1624560,"uid":76960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:16:18.000Z","msg":"推，大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51faff9d9ad790a164ba2f9233ea0fd751eac8d","tid":1624560,"uid":76960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa19093f76a1b8e8449887f0ace8e663cc01db0","tid":1624560,"uid":76960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"推推推推推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" clas